News Releases, Media Advisories

Mary 30, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON THE NORTH DAKOTA DEMOCRATIC – NONPARTISAN LEAGUE PARTY
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on the North Dakota Democratic – Nonpartisan League Party. This audit covers the period of January 1, 1999 through December 31, 2000.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
title: FEC Releases Final Audit Report on the North Dakota Democratic - Nonpartisan League Party
